text: Phoebemima antiqua is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1889. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Phoebemima antiqua. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1889
title: Phoebemima antiqua
